---
title: Falafel Power Bowls Spinach, Creamy Dressing & Garlicky Pita
description: Get ready for dinner in a flash! This Mediterranean-inspired, plant-based meal is full of flavor, simple to make, and will be on your table in 15 minutes or less. You’ll shallow-fry falafel—spiced chickpea croquettes—to a crispy finish and serve over a bed of spinach with juicy tomatoes, briny feta, fresh dill, and earthy red pepper hummus. Finish with a drizzle of garlicky white sauce and sprinkle with almonds for extra flavor and crunch. Fluffy, garlicky pita completes this speedy, savory meal.
